---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
	<main>
		<h1 class="mt-6">Engineering</h1>
        <h2>Printer Plant, Planter Print!</h2>
		<div class="instructions  bg-slate-800">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">
                1) Double Dimond Model
                <span class="text-xs">
                    Mark fortæller (Max 10 min)
                </span>
            </h3>
            <img class="max-w-sm mt-4" src="https://innovationenglish.sites.ku.dk/files/2016/08/Double-diamond_ENG.jpg" alt=""><br>
			<a href="https://www.printables.com/model/230363-leaf-drink-coasters-with-decorative-plant-holder#preview">
				<p>
					Fallback design-projekt
				</p>
			</a>
        </div>
        <div class="instructions bg-slate-800">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">
                Teknikøvelser
				<span class="text-xs">
					Fra sidste gang...
				</span>
            </h3>
			<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G5NVSOWDqco">
			
				<p>
					Øvelse 1: Boks med et net af huller
				</p>
			</a>
			<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GI3BFimvVV8">
				<p>
					Øvelse 2: Spejled form med skruehuller
				</p>
			
			</a>
			<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TaxvtUXtw7g">
			</a>
			<p>
				Øvelse 3: Blad med bexier streger/huller i
			</p>
				
        </div>
		<div class="instructions bg-slate-800">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">
                Vælg en type plante at designe
				<span class="text-xs">
					Hvilken plante skal jeg designe..?
				</span>
            </h3>
			<p>
				1) Hvilken plante vil du designe? - Undersøg formen på den plante.
			</p>
			<p class="text-sm">
				Bonus: Skal den kunne noget særligt eller noget ekstra?
			</p><br>
			<p>
				2) Hvilken del vil du designe først? Eks. blad eller base.
			</p>
			<p>
				3) Papir-skitse: Tegn en MEGET grov skitse på papir.
			</p>
			<p>
				4) Fra skitse til prototype i Onshape (Print så snart du er klar).
			</p>
        </div>
		<div class="instructions bg-slate-900">
			<h3>Øvelser af konkrete teknikker
				<span class="text-xs">
					Du måske få brug for i dit projekt.
				</span>
			</h3>
			<a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=3d+print+joints&rlz=1C1GCEB_enDK1099DK1100&oq=3d+print+joints&gs_lcrp=EgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOdIBCDU0NzFqMGo5qAIAsAIB&sourceid=chrome&ie=UTF-8#fpstate=ive&vld=cid:72a867c2,vid:RTQjvYENR7w,st:0">
				<p>
					About slot joints
				</p>
			</a>
			<a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=ball+joint+onshape&rlz=1C1GCEB_enDK1099DK1100&oq=ball+joint+onshape&gs_lcrp=EgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOdIBCDI1MjdqMGo3qAIAsAIA&sourceid=chrome&ie=UTF-8#fpstate=ive&vld=cid:62d9c272,vid:pMzNV-pzSFs,st:0">
				<p>
					Ball-socket joint
				</p>
			</a>
			<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cKmhDlWDyM0">
				<p>
					Extrude lines (Kaffekop hank/håndtag)
				</p>
			</a>
			<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cKmhDlWDyM0">
				<p>
					Holes in sphere (Golfball)
				</p>
			</a>
			<a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=onshape+to+part+together&rlz=1C1GCEB_enDK1099DK1100&oq=onshape+to+part+together&gs_lcrp=EgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOdIBCDUwMzlqMGo5qAIAsAIB&sourceid=chrome&ie=UTF-8#fpstate=ive&vld=cid:8cca631d,vid:kKsVUTRPM3k,st:0">
				<p>
					Designeing multiple parts together
				</p>
			</a>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.instructions p, .instructions h3:not(.inspiration){
		margin-bottom: 12px;
	}
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		width: 800px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: white;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	.astro-a {
		position: absolute;
		top: -32px;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translatex(-50%);
		width: 220px;
		height: auto;
		z-index: -1;
	}
	h1,h2 {
		
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: center;
		
	}

    h1{
        font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
    }

    h2{
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }
	.text-gradient {
		background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}
	.instructions {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 25%);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
	}

	.instructions.color{
		background: linear-gradient(rgba(var(--accent-dark), 66%), rgba(var(--accent-dark), 33%));
	}
	.instructions code {
		font-size: 0.8em;
		font-weight: bold;
		background: rgba(var(--accent-light), 12%);
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		border-radius: 4px;
		padding: 0.3em 0.4em;
	}
    .instructions p{
        margin-left:64px;
    }
	.instructions strong {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
	}
	.link-card-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(1fr, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 0;
	}
</style>